<li class='cover' id='bookCover_15954557'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15954557-on-the-train"><img alt="On the Train" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1349149557l/15954557._SX98_.jpg" />
